    4388.75n 1.8 4398.5n 0 4408.25n 1.8 4418n 0 4427.75n 1.8 4437.5n 0 \
    4447.25n 1.8 4457n 0 4466.75n 1.8 4476.5n 0 4486.25n 1.8 4496n 0 \
    4505.75n 1.8 4515.5n 0 4525.25n 1.8 4535n 0 4544.75n 1.8 4554.5n 0 \
    4564.25n 1.8 4574n 0 4583.75n 1.8 4593.5n 0 4603.25n 1.8 4613n 0 \
